  U+0A4C U+0A71 U+200C > U+0A14 U+0A71 c au

  any(vyanjan) U+0A05 U+0A71 U+200C > context(1) U+0A3E U+0A71 c aa
  any(vyanjan) U+0A07 U+0A71 U+200C > context(1) U+0A3F U+0A71 c i
  any(vyanjan) U+0A08 U+0A71 U+200C > context(1) U+0A40 U+0A71 c ii
  any(vyanjan) U+0A09 U+0A71 U+200C > context(1) U+0A41 U+0A71 c u
  any(vyanjan) U+0A0A U+0A71 U+200C > context(1) U+0A42 U+0A71 c uu
  any(vyanjan) U+0A0F U+0A71 U+200C > context(1) U+0A47 U+0A71 c e
  any(vyanjan) U+0A10 U+0A71 U+200C > context(1) U+0A48 U+0A71 c ai
  any(vyanjan) U+0A13 U+0A71 U+200C > context(1) U+0A4B U+0A71 c o
  any(vyanjan) U+0A14 U+0A71 U+200C > context(1) U+0A4C U+0A71 c au

  c vyanjan + adak bindi +ZWNJ = vyanjan + a + adak bindi
  any(vyanjan) U+0A01 U+200C > context(1) U+0A05 U+0A01
  c vyanjan + bindu +ZWNJ = vyanjan + a + bindu
  any(vyanjan) U+0A02 U+200C > context(1) U+0A05 U+0A02
  c vyanjan + tippi +ZWNJ = vyanjan + a + tippi
  any(vyanjan) U+0A70 U+200C > context(1) U+0A05 U+0A70
  c vyanjan + addak +ZWNJ = vyanjan + a + addak
  any(vyanjan) U+0A71 U+200C > context(1) U+0A05 U+0A71
  any(vyanjan) U+200C  > context(1) c remove zwnj if adding another vyanjan
  any(svara) U+200C  > context(1) c remove zwnj if adding another svara
  U+200C U+200C > U+200C c only one zwnj
  U+0020 U+200C > U+0020 c if nothing behind, just don't add zwnj
  nul U+200C > nul c if nothing behind, do nothing.

group(handleNuqta)
  U+0A16 U+0A3C > U+0A59 c kha -> khha
  U+0A17 U+0A3C > U+0A5A c ga -> ghha
  U+0A1C U+0A3C > U+0A5B c ja -> za
  U+0A2B U+0A3C > U+0A5E c pha -> fa
  U+0A38 U+0A3C > U+0A36 c sa -> sha
  U+0A32 U+0A3C > U+0A33 c la -> lla

  c reverse order handling
  U+0A59 U+0A3C > U+0A16
  U+0A5A U+0A3C > U+0A17
  U+0A5B U+0A3C > U+0A1C
  U+0A5E U+0A3C > U+0A2B
  U+0A36 U+0A3C > U+0A38
  U+0A33 U+0A3C > U+0A32

  c when in front of nuqta (need to reverse order for matra conversion to work)
  U+0A4D U+0A3C > U+0A3C U+0A4D c a
  U+0A3E U+0A3C > U+0A3C U+0A3E c aa
  U+0A3F U+0A3C > U+0A3C U+0A3F c i
  U+0A41 U+0A3C > U+0A3C U+0A41 c u
  U+0A47 U+0A3C > U+0A3C U+0A47 c e
  U+0A4B U+0A3C > U+0A3C U+0A4B c o
